Implementing / maintaining / improvement of the quality system in the specific area of responsibility;
Coordination of the activity of the employees in order to accomplish the relevant Q-targets in production;
Insuring that the customer requirements, applicable standards for the system/process/product are found in the internal documentation, are implemented and respected;
Support in making process, product and customer audits: sustaining, documenting, evaluation, reporting and reaction;
Participation at the customer complaints analysis and proposal of corrective actions.

